Command> gh pr comment

Arguments> [issue number]

TL;DR> プルリクにコメント

Keywords> github

Description>
           > -b, --body <text>
           > -F, --body-file <file>
           > --edit-last
           >    edit the last comment of the same author
           > -e, --editor
           > -w, --web

Scene> gh pr comment 13 --body "Hi from GitHub CLI"


Reference> https://cli.github.com/manual/gh_pr_comment
